{"type": "article", "id": 61886, "title": "陈漫为快手拍“八仙过海”广告照，一波女性主题活动发布 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-08T06:03:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 137, "name": "女性"}, {"id": 46776, "name": "快手"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190308131304RaWdEFyOnJVo0P5c.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"CCu6\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4347229752437586?\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>邓伦成为九阳品牌代言人，</b></a>之前代言人是杨幂。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131407jF6eHphBdPwKWV32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.688608\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"Dq4B\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Buubgh-glWN/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>adidas 和韩国艺术家 Jen Bartel 合作推出“惊奇队长”主题的联名鞋款 adidas AM4。</b></a>鞋面采用了红金配色，鞋头以三道金纹设计了宇宙星辰的图案。这款鞋将于今日《惊奇队长》上映之际，在 footlocker 发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131425OTCwergYKWo9yZ70.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131426KH6kfORWPxrebYXA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"hEL8\"><b><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Buubgh-glWN/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">美的空调也推出了漫威系列定制款空调</a>，</b>分别是蜘蛛侠款和美国队长款。联名款空调已经在 3 月 6 日的苏宁超级品牌活动日上开始限量销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u08440e4hfx\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131500auY7oj0WQqxVSX4U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"GU8p\">惊奇队长选择了 3 月 8 日这个时间上映，借此来和电影主角是女性超级英雄呼应。<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4347146704280218?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">不过昨天漫威影业发布了一条庆祝“女生节快乐”的微博。这一祝福引发了不小的负面评论。</a>有人认为，女生节其实在加深男女不平等的现象，和电影强调的女性独立不相符。</p><p line=\"HpyX\">不过今天又发布了妇女节的官方祝福，以及最新一条微博是庆祝票房破亿。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131627YqthGkC96M7SPxul.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654611\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131526WIGAtuOrH5NsQeEh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.722667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131611ohqNQscuOEZGfy95.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.725333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"YTTA\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4346798858358547?\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>快手和短视频 App 大片合作推出了“八仙过海”主题的摄影广告。</b></a>由大片 App 创始人之一陈漫拍摄，快手工耿、最潮刘老头等 8 位快手红人正好和八仙对应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131648r92ZLxeTUOvDfXqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.841667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903081316476eFHUruWdkAlv2L5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903081316483gTFXEDQBaiOWjcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131649VlCdn3vUPtgIBAzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131648NUAVm28LjMGladDH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903081316495wuFmIfvOTgXCG9i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131649XYMEgD1j96l4Bb5J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131649ow9Uh2xy5Cv18en4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131650OuCHvAn7akj3MXE9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"eaKr\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/3232338382/4347146570509397\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美柚的女生节活动是让男性来体验女性生理期的痛感。</b></a>体验结束后与参与的男性和职场女性进行对话，希望男朋友可以在女性生理期多些理解。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0845mmvafm\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t\r\n</div><p line=\"IrVb\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4347505259459754?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>上海迪士“尼”乐园的标牌为了庆祝妇女节变成了上海迪士“妮”乐园，</b></a>上面还缀了个米妮的标示性蝴蝶结。此外，园区内也针对妇女节进行了相应的改造。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131732EQmHK420LeV9UPjO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131733IQah5STsVOXfb9NB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030813173358hIwg9ySWlefb1d.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903081317327wDNldeOvCFnVbRB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131732jM0srECKbwx8NQaV.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p line=\"eMJV\"><b>美图在上海静安大悦城举办了关于女性成长的摄影展。</b>每个展馆内都会展出 6 幅摄影作品，全部是由美图秀秀的用户拍摄。在场馆内分成六个不同风格的区域，鼓励参与者自拍。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131813IMtm2Np814Fueqsb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743326\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190308131813Fe7LyjoxOkKZNwqR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.444444\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p line=\"kMgZ\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gfag2c-8eGU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>adidas 昨天发布了妇女节广告 <em>She Breaks Barriers: More Visibility. Bigger Dreams.</em></b></a>品牌从媒介播放角度讲述了女性运动，越来越多的媒体报道女性在赛场上的表现，才可能逐渐消除性别之间的不平等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\"> \t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r0846bzudsc\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe> \t</figure> \t\r\n</div><p line=\"e7rC\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/QDpkA34xsNc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>梅赛德斯奔驰的广告片展现了历史上第一次汽车自驾旅程中的场景。</b></a>创始人 Carl Benz 的妻子和商业伙伴 Bertha Benz 被广泛认为是第一位司机，片中她的车子在途中出了故障，到药房寻找替代燃料，还用袜带为燃料管线保温。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=j0846whxwmj\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"wikW\"><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/in-n-out-sues-puma-sneakers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国精品汉堡品牌 In-N-Out 起诉彪马侵权。</b></a>它控告彪马 Cali-O Drive Thru 鞋带上的设计抄袭了自己的棕榈树设计，两者看起来很相似。</p><p line=\"wikW\">而且这款新鞋 2 月份上市的时候，彪马还推出 3 支汉堡主题的广告片。这种刻意和汉堡构建联系的宣传方式，In-N-Out 认为会让消费者产生误解。它要求彪马在赔偿损失之外，还要支付新鞋款获得的利润。</p><p line=\"JvJq\"><a href=\"https://venturebeat.com/2019/03/06/google-is-giving-users-in-app-rewards-for-watching-ads/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google 为 Android用户在新游戏中推出广告奖励形式。</b></a>玩家观看一段视频后可以获得奖励，不过奖励必须超过 10 美元才能提现。目前这仍然是测试版，并且只支持视频形式。</p><p line=\"7dks\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/fX1_vECihxU?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">roya ann miller</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/women-hero?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}